---
import {
  opedAnnualRuptures,
  opedCannotSleepPct,
  opedSleepMarketCopy,
  opedSplintSales,
} from "@/features/oped-deck/opedDeckContent";
---

<div class="bg-primary/5 p-5 border border-primary/25 rounded-xl">
  <p class="mb-3 font-semibold text-slate-800 text-sm">Market scale</p>
  <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
    <strong class="text-slate-800">{opedCannotSleepPct}% cannot sleep</strong> in
    the boot (Thetis patient survey). In the US, UK, Germany, France, Australia,
    and Canada alone there are {opedSleepMarketCopy.annualRupturesLabel} Achilles
    ruptures per year - about {opedSleepMarketCopy.cannotSleepLabel} patients who
    struggle to sleep in a walking boot.
  </p>
  <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
    Thetis currently supplies {opedSleepMarketCopy.splintSalesLabel} night splints
    in those regions ({opedSplintSales.us.toLocaleString("en-GB")} US,{" "}
    {opedSplintSales.uk.toLocaleString("en-GB")} UK,{" "}
    {opedSplintSales.ca.toLocaleString("en-GB")} Canada), leaving roughly{" "}
    <strong class="text-primary">{opedSleepMarketCopy.unmetNeedLabel}</strong> boot
    patients without a dedicated sleep solution each year.
  </p>
</div>
